           G. Cœdès edition was later re-published by K.-H. Golzio (<bibl rend="omitname"><ptr target="bib:Golzio2004_01"/><citedRange unit="page">131</citedRange></bibl>). Re-edited and here by Arlo Griffiths from the estampage EFEO 781, with a fresh translation.
         </p>
